conversation.text: Hello, this is Divya from Kainskep Solutions
Hi.
Is this a good time to talk for a few minutes?
Hi.
Is this a good time to talk for a few minutes?
No.
Sure, when would be a better time to connect?
I can't tell you.
I understand. Could you please let me know when you're available for a quick call? I’ll make sure to reach out at a convenient time for you.
Okay. Mm, I am available now.
Great, thank you for confirming. I’ll keep this brief and get straight to the point. How are you doing today?
Good.
That’s wonderful to hear. The purpose of this call is regarding potential career opportunities with us. May I know if you are currently exploring new job opportunities?
Yeah.
Perfect, thank you for letting me know. May I know which domain and role you are currently looking for?
Uh, yes. Uh, I'm looking for a role, uh, I am a front-end developer, but I have mostly coded in Angular. Uh, so I am looking for a front-end developer roles where Angular is required.
Thank you for sharing that. We do have opportunities in the front-end development domain, particularly for roles involving Angular. May I know your current location?
Ah, yeah, my city is Delhi.
I see. This is a strictly in-office role based in Jaipur. Would you be comfortable relocating to Jaipur for this position?
Yeah.
That’s great to hear. Thank you for confirming your willingness to relocate. Could you please share your current notice period?
It is one twenty days.
Thank you for sharing. Our hiring process prefers candidates who can join within 30 days. Is your notice period negotiable?
Mm-hmm. There is a buyout option in my company.
That’s good to know. Thank you for confirming that the notice period is negotiable. Could you please share your total experience in years?
I did not say that the notice period is negotiable, uh, but I did say that it-- uh, there is a buyout option available.
I understand. You mentioned there’s a buyout option available, which could help in reducing the notice period. Just to confirm, would you be able to join within 30 days if the buyout is processed?
Yes, I can.
Excellent. Thank you for confirming. Could you please share your current company and current role?
Uh, current company is Skin Skip Solution, uh, and my CTC-- my role is, uh, uh, developer.
Thank you for sharing. Could you please confirm your current CTC in LPA?
It is five.
Got it. What would be your expected CTC for your next opportunity?
Around seven to eight.
Your expected CTC seems slightly above our current budget for this role. Is your salary negotiable?
No, it is not negotiable because, uh, I am already a experienced person. So, uh, seven LPA is a very low amount that I am asking. Low salary that I am asking from you.
